---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';

const posts = (await getCollection('blog'))
  .filter(p => p.data.featured)
  .sort((a, b) => new Date(b.data.date).getTime() - new Date(a.data.date).getTime())
  .slice(0, 3);
---

<Base
  title="SafetyTAP"
  metaTitle="Hazard Recognition Training That Works | SafetyTAP"
  description="SafetyTAP builds hazard recognition skills in 30 seconds — no app, no training, just a photo and a text. Built for construction crews."
>

  <!-- Section 1: Hero — z-stacked cinematic layout -->
  <section class="relative block min-h-[80vh] overflow-hidden text-white" style="background-color: #0b1221">

    <!-- Layer 1 (z-10): Hero image — absolute, right-aligned, CSS mask fade -->
    <div
      class="hidden md:block absolute top-0 right-0 bottom-0 w-[80%]"
      style="z-index: 10; -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, transparent 20%, black 50%); mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, transparent 20%, black 50%)"
    >
      <img
        src="/images/send_it_to_safetytap.jpg"
        alt="Construction worker in gloves holding a phone showing SafetyTAP on a job site"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        style="object-position: 75% center; filter: brightness(0.85)"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <!-- Bottom gradient fade into next section -->
      <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-40" style="background: linear-gradient(to top, #0b1221, transparent)"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Layer 2 (z-20): Text content — vertically centered -->
    <div class="relative flex items-center min-h-[80vh] px-6" style="z-index: 20">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full">
        <div class="max-w-[600px]">
          <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight">Build Hazard Recognition Skills Your Crew Will Actually Use</h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-teal font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">Think. Assess. Proceed.</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 leading-relaxed">In 30 seconds, your crew texts a photo and gets one specific safety observation back — the kind an experienced pro would make on-site. No app, no training, no friction.</p>

          <!-- [PLACEHOLDER — replace with real customer quote] -->
          <div class="mt-6 border-l-2 border-teal/40 pl-4">
            <p class="text-white/60 text-sm italic">"We saw a change in how crews talked about hazards within the first month."</p>
            <p class="text-white/40 text-xs mt-1">— [PLACEHOLDER] Safety Director, Mid-size General Contractor</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4 mt-8">
            <a href="/try"
               class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-teal hover:bg-teal-light
                      text-white font-semibold text-base
                      px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg
                      shadow-lg shadow-teal/20
                      transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-teal/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5">
              Try It Now
            </a>
            <a href="/contact"
               class="inline-flex items-center gap-2
                      border border-white/30 hover:border-white/60
                      text-white/90 hover:text-white font-medium text-base
                      px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg
                      transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-white/5 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-white/5">
              Request a Demo
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mobile: full-bleed image below text -->
    <div class="md:hidden relative">
      <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0b1221] to-transparent" style="z-index: 5"></div>
      <img
        src="/images/send_it_to_safetytap.jpg"
        alt="Construction worker in gloves holding a phone showing SafetyTAP on a job site"
        class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
        style="object-position: right center; filter: brightness(0.85)"
        loading="eager"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: The Problem — #3: Dark background treatment -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-[#1a1f2e]" data-animate data-stagger-delay="0.1">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-teal mb-3" data-stagger>The Problem</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white leading-tight tracking-tight" data-stagger>Your safety program creates compliance. It doesn't create competence.</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-lg text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
        <p data-stagger>Your crew fills out JHAs because they have to. They sit through toolbox talks because it's on the schedule. They check the boxes on the observation card because someone's counting. None of it changes how they actually see hazards when they're standing in front of the task.</p>
        <p data-stagger>The problem isn't the people. Every safety observation program on the market was designed to document compliance, not develop hazard recognition. They assume the worker already knows what to look for. Most of the time, that assumption is wrong.</p>
        <p data-stagger>It's not that your program is bad. It's that the problem is deeper than any program can reach.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: The Insight -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-teal-pale" data-animate data-stagger-delay="0.1">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-teal mb-3" data-stagger>Our Approach</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy leading-tight tracking-tight" data-stagger>Hazard recognition isn't a checklist. It's a skill.</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-lg text-dark/80 leading-relaxed">
        <p data-stagger>Experienced workers develop what the industry calls "the eye" — the ability to walk onto a site and immediately spot what's off. It's not magic. It's hazard identification skills built through years of exposure and mentoring from people who know what matters.</p>
        <p data-stagger>SafetyTAP accelerates that process. Like scaffolding on a building — you erect it to support the work, and you take it down when the structure can stand on its own.</p>
      </div>
      <blockquote class="relative pl-8 py-2 my-8 border-l-4 border-teal" data-stagger>
        <span class="absolute -left-1 -top-3 text-5xl text-teal/20 font-serif leading-none select-none">"</span>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl italic font-medium text-navy leading-relaxed">A worker who stops using SafetyTAP because they no longer need it is our greatest success.</p>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: How It Works — Scrollytelling sticky-track -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="relative" style="background-color: #0b1221;">

    <!-- Environmental background blobs -->
    <div class="hiw-blob-container">
      <div class="hiw-blob" data-parallax-speed="0.03"
           style="width: 600px; height: 600px; background: #4fd1c5; top: 5%; left: -10%;"></div>
      <div class="hiw-blob" data-parallax-speed="-0.02"
           style="width: 500px; height: 500px; background: #2A9D8F; top: 40%; right: -8%;"></div>
      <div class="hiw-blob" data-parallax-speed="0.015"
           style="width: 400px; height: 400px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4fd1c5, #2A9D8F); bottom: 10%; left: -5%;"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section header (mobile only — desktop header is inside sticky viewport) -->
    <div class="md:hidden text-center px-6 pt-10 pb-4" style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3" style="color: #4fd1c5;">How It Works</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white leading-tight tracking-tight">30 seconds. One text. Zero friction.</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Desktop: Scrollytelling pinned-stage layout -->
    <div id="hiw-track" class="hidden md:block relative" style="height: 220vh;">

      <!-- Scroll sentinels (invisible, drive IntersectionObserver) -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="hiw-sentinel" data-step="1" style="height: 33.33%;"></div>
        <div class="hiw-sentinel" data-step="2" style="height: 33.33%;"></div>
        <div class="hiw-sentinel" data-step="3" style="height: 34%;"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sticky viewport — pinned below fixed nav for the full scroll track -->
      <div class="sticky flex flex-col" style="top: 76px; height: calc(100vh - 76px); z-index: 1;">

        <!-- Pinned section header (stays visible throughout all steps) -->
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 text-center px-6 pt-6 pb-3 2xl:pt-8 2xl:pb-4" style="z-index: 2;">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-2" style="color: #4fd1c5;">How It Works</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white leading-tight tracking-tight">30 seconds. One text. Zero friction.</h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Content row (fills remaining space below header) -->
        <div class="flex items-start flex-1 w-full px-6 gap-8 2xl:gap-12 pt-2" style="max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto;">

          <!-- Progress Track -->
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 relative self-stretch" style="width: 48px;">
            <!-- Background line -->
            <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[2px] h-full rounded-full" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);"></div>
            <!-- Fill line -->
            <div id="hiw-fill" class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[2px] rounded-full" style="background: #4fd1c5; height: 0%; top: 0; transition: height 0.35s ease-out;"></div>
            <!-- Step dots -->
            <div class="hiw-dot absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2" data-dot="1" style="top: 0%;"></div>
            <div class="hiw-dot absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2" data-dot="2" style="top: 50%;"></div>
            <div class="hiw-dot absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2" data-dot="3" style="top: 100%;"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Text Stage (all 3 steps stacked, cross-fade in place) -->
          <div class="relative self-stretch" style="flex: 1 1 40%; max-width: 520px;">
            <div class="hiw-step absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center" data-step="1">
              <p class="text-7xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold font-display leading-none select-none" style="color: #4fd1c5;">01</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mt-2 leading-tight">Take a photo</h3>
              <p class="text-white/55 mt-3 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-sm">Snap a photo of the task or work area. Five seconds. No special app — just the phone camera they already carry.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hiw-step absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center" data-step="2">
              <p class="text-7xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold font-display leading-none select-none" style="color: #4fd1c5;">02</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mt-2 leading-tight">Send it to SafetyTAP</h3>
              <p class="text-white/55 mt-3 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-sm">Text the photo on Telegram. No download, no account, no login. If they can send a text, they can use it.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hiw-step absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center" data-step="3">
              <p class="text-7xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold font-display leading-none select-none" style="color: #4fd1c5;">03</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mt-2 leading-tight">Get one observation</h3>
              <p class="text-white/55 mt-3 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-sm">In seconds, one specific thing to check — the kind of call an experienced safety pro would make standing right next to you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Phone mockup -->
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex justify-center items-center">

            <!-- iPhone device frame -->
            <div id="hiw-phone" class="hiw-phone-frame relative flex flex-col"
                 style="width: 340px; height: 80vh; max-height: 720px;
                        background: #1a1a1a;
                        border-radius: 50px;
                        padding: 12px;">

              <!-- Side buttons -->
              <div class="absolute -right-[2px] top-[120px] w-[3px] h-[44px] bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-r-sm"></div>
              <div class="absolute -left-[2px] top-[95px] w-[3px] h-[28px] bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-l-sm"></div>
              <div class="absolute -left-[2px] top-[135px] w-[3px] h-[44px] bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-l-sm"></div>
              <div class="absolute -left-[2px] top-[190px] w-[3px] h-[44px] bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-l-sm"></div>

              <!-- Screen area -->
              <div class="relative flex-1 flex flex-col rounded-[38px] overflow-hidden bg-[#1a1a2e]">

                <!-- Dynamic Island -->
                <div class="absolute top-[10px] left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-30 w-[100px] h-[28px] bg-black rounded-full"
                     style="box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.05) inset;"></div>

                <!-- Glass overlay -->
                <div class="absolute inset-0 z-20 pointer-events-none rounded-[38px]"
                     style="background:
                       linear-gradient(125deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 15%, transparent 40%),
                       linear-gradient(235deg, transparent 60%, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 85%, rgba(255,255,255,0.06) 100%);"></div>

                <!-- Dark-mode Telegram header -->
                <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-3 px-4 pt-[44px] pb-3" style="background: #1e2c3a;">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white/70" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
                  <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: #2A9D8F;">
                    <img src="/logo-icon.svg" alt="" class="w-5 h-5" />
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                      <p class="text-white text-[15px] font-semibold leading-tight">SafetyTAP</p>
                      <span class="text-[10px] font-medium px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-white/70" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">bot</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-white/40 text-xs leading-tight mt-0.5">last seen recently</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Chat body: additive bubbles synced to scroll -->
                <div id="hiw-chat-body" class="relative z-10 flex-1 overflow-hidden p-3.5" style="background: #0e1621;">

                  <!-- Bubble 1: Photo message (visible on step 1+) -->
                  <div class="hiw-bubble flex justify-end mb-3" data-bubble="1">
                    <div class="rounded-2xl rounded-tr-sm p-1.5 shadow-md" style="max-width: 88%; background: #2b5278;">
                      <img src="/images/take_a_photo.jpg" alt="Jobsite photo" class="w-full rounded-xl object-cover" style="max-height: 200px;" loading="lazy" />
                      <p class="text-[13px] text-white/90 mt-1.5 px-2 leading-snug">Check this area before we start</p>
                      <p class="text-[11px] text-white/40 text-right mt-0.5 px-2">9:41 AM <span class="ml-0.5">&#10003;&#10003;</span></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <!-- Bubble 2: Typing indicator (visible on step 2 only) -->
                  <div class="hiw-bubble flex justify-start mb-3" data-bubble="2">
                    <div>
                      <div class="rounded-2xl rounded-tl-sm px-4 py-3 shadow-md" style="background: #182533;">
                        <div class="flex gap-1.5 items-center">
                          <span class="w-[7px] h-[7px] rounded-full animate-bounce-dot" style="background: #4fd1c5;"></span>
                          <span class="w-[7px] h-[7px] rounded-full animate-bounce-dot" style="background: #4fd1c5; animation-delay: 0.15s;"></span>
                          <span class="w-[7px] h-[7px] rounded-full animate-bounce-dot" style="background: #4fd1c5; animation-delay: 0.3s;"></span>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <p class="text-[12px] text-center mt-2 animate-pulse-text" style="color: #4fd1c5;">SafetyTAP is analyzing...</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <!-- Bubble 3: AI observation response (visible on step 3) -->
                  <div class="hiw-bubble flex justify-start" data-bubble="3">
                    <div class="rounded-2xl rounded-tl-sm p-3.5 shadow-md" style="max-width: 92%; background: #182533;">
                      <p class="text-[14px] leading-relaxed" style="color: #e1e1e1;">Trip hazard at the western access point — ensure rebar caps are in place and all tools are stored clear of the walking path before the crew moves through.</p>
                      <p class="text-[11px] text-right mt-2" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">9:41 AM</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                </div>

                <!-- Chat input bar -->
                <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2.5" style="background: #1e2c3a;">
                  <div class="flex-1 rounded-full px-4 py-2" style="background: #0e1621;">
                    <p class="text-[13px]" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">Message</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: #2A9D8F;">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M2.01 21L23 12 2.01 3 2 10l15 2-15 2z"/></svg>
                  </div>
                </div>

              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Scroll-to-explore indicator -->
        <div id="hiw-scroll-hint" class="absolute flex flex-col items-center gap-1" style="bottom: 24px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);">
          <span class="text-xs font-medium tracking-wider uppercase">Scroll</span>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mobile: stacked steps + static chat preview -->
    <div class="md:hidden px-6 pb-10">
      <div class="space-y-10 mt-6" style="max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div>
          <p class="text-5xl font-extrabold font-display leading-none select-none" style="color: #4fd1c5;">01</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-1">Take a photo</h3>
          <p class="text-white/55 mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed">Snap a photo of the task or work area. Five seconds. No special app — just the phone camera they already carry.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-5xl font-extrabold font-display leading-none select-none" style="color: #4fd1c5;">02</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-1">Send it to SafetyTAP</h3>
          <p class="text-white/55 mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed">Text the photo on Telegram. No download, no account, no login. If they can send a text, they can use it.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-5xl font-extrabold font-display leading-none select-none" style="color: #4fd1c5;">03</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-1">Get one observation</h3>
          <p class="text-white/55 mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed">In seconds, one specific thing to check — the kind of call an experienced safety pro would make standing right next to you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-4 space-y-3 mt-8" style="max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; background: #0e1621;">
        <div class="flex justify-end">
          <div class="rounded-2xl rounded-tr-sm p-1.5 shadow-md" style="max-width: 85%; background: #2b5278;">
            <img src="/images/take_a_photo.jpg" alt="Jobsite photo" class="w-full rounded-xl object-cover" style="max-height: 160px;" loading="lazy" />
            <p class="text-sm mt-1 px-2 leading-snug" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">Check this area before we start</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-start">
          <div class="rounded-2xl rounded-tl-sm p-3 shadow-md" style="max-width: 90%; background: #182533;">
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #e1e1e1;">Trip hazard at the western access point — ensure rebar caps are in place and all tools are stored clear of the walking path.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom text -->
    <div class="text-center px-6 pb-16">
      <p class="text-white/40 text-base leading-relaxed">No app to download. No account to create. No training required.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: The Science — #5: Permanent left accent + hover bg wash -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-light" data-animate data-stagger-delay="0.12">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-teal mb-3 text-center" data-stagger>The Science</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy text-center leading-tight tracking-tight" data-stagger>The science behind better hazard recognition</h2>
      <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out group border-l-[3px] border-l-teal hover:bg-teal/[0.04]" data-stagger>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-navy mb-2 group-hover:text-teal transition-colors">Inattentional Blindness</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">Workers focused on their task literally cannot see hazards outside their focus area — the brain filters them out. SafetyTAP breaks that tunnel vision with one targeted observation before the task begins.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out group border-l-[3px] border-l-teal hover:bg-teal/[0.04]" data-stagger>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-navy mb-2 group-hover:text-teal transition-colors">Self-Efficacy</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">Workers who believe their actions can prevent incidents engage in more proactive safety behavior. Confidence drives competence. Each SafetyTAP interaction builds that confidence through specific, actionable feedback.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out group border-l-[3px] border-l-teal hover:bg-teal/[0.04]" data-stagger>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-navy mb-2 group-hover:text-teal transition-colors">Normalcy Bias</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">When unsafe conditions persist without incident, the brain reclassifies them as normal. "We've always done it this way" is the result. SafetyTAP surfaces what familiarity has made invisible.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out group border-l-[3px] border-l-teal hover:bg-teal/[0.04]" data-stagger>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-navy mb-2 group-hover:text-teal transition-colors">Bystander Effect</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">The larger the crew, the less likely anyone is to speak up about a concern. SafetyTAP is a private channel that removes the social cost.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-teal hover:text-teal-light font-medium underline-offset-2 hover:underline transition-colors">Read: Why Workers Miss Hazards — And What Actually Helps</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 6: What Makes It Different — #6: Comparison table added -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white" data-animate data-stagger-delay="0.1">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-teal mb-3" data-stagger>What's Different</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy leading-tight tracking-tight" data-stagger>Not another program. A practice.</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-lg text-dark/80 leading-relaxed">
